## How It Works

1. This agent registers with `capability="llm"` on the mesh
2. Other agents with `@MeshLlm(providerSelector = @Selector(capability = "llm"))` discover this provider
3. LLM requests are routed through the mesh to this provider
4. This provider forwards requests to the LLM API via Spring AI

